snippet.title: Hatsune Miku Has Arrived with Festival Season 7!
snippet.description:
The first Sound from the Future is here! Hatsune Miku has arrived with Fortnite Festival Season 7! 

Unlock a Hatsune Miku Outfit, Instruments, and more in the Music Pass, which is now a single track of both free and premium rewards (matching the other Passes in Fortnite). You can purchase the Music Pass for 1,400 V-Bucks or get it through Fortnite Crew. 

Read more: https://fn.gg/FestivalS7

Follow Fortnite Festival on social media:
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/fnfestival
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@fnfestival
